data.description: Beautiful three bedroom two bath home in sought after Gila Buttes in Casa Grande! Amazing open floor plan with primary suite split from other bedrooms. Gorgeous kitchen with ginormous island and breakfast bar! Stainless steal appliances, large walk-in pantry, granite counter tops, upgraded fixtures. Open living room for relaxation and/or entertainment. Perfect primary suite with dual sinks, walk in shower, and large walk-in closet. Covered back patio and double gate too! On North end of Casa Grande, so close to I10 for commute to Phoenix!
